  <answerContent><![CDATA[<h3>For payment and ticketing enquiries</h3>
<p>If you have any questions about payments or ticketing please contact us on:</p>
<p><strong>Payments</strong>: <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 166</span><br /><strong>Ticketing:</strong> <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 122</span> or email <a href="mailto:beforeyoutravel@inghams.co.uk">beforeyoutravel@inghams.co.uk</a></p>
<p>Or you can complete the customer contact form below and select the 'Before You Go' option.</p>
<h3>Opening hours:</h3>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Monday - Friday: </strong>9am – 6:00pm</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Saturday</strong>: 9am – 5:30pm</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Sunday</strong>: Closed</p>
<p>Please note that your holiday documents will be sent to you within 14 days of your departure.</p>]]></answerContent>
